Inigo Pierce von Syberg Tibaldi Lenderking
Inigo Pierce Syberg Tibaldi Lenderking (born August 2, 2006) is the youngest documented descendant of the German noble von Syberg family.He is the son of Eben Pierce Lenderking and Tanja Astrid Dagny Tibaldi and has an elder brother, Barnabe Wentworth Benito Tibaldi Lenderking. Notable ancestors includes direct lineage from Christian Friederich Wilhelm Heinrich "Felix" von Syberg (1785â€“1864)of the Westphalian Freiherr and Ritter lineage, and indirect lineage from Friedrich Von Syberg.
